fields.calculatedFormula:
IF( NOT(TicketableEvent__r.Active__c), "Retired (Event)",
IF( NOT(Active__c), "Retired (Instance)",
IF( SaleStartDate__c >  NOW(), "Not on sale yet",
IF( AND(ISBLANK(SaleEndDate__c), InstanceDate__c < NOW()), "No longer on sale",
IF( SaleEndDate__c < NOW(), "No longer on sale",
"On Sale")))))
fields.inlineHelpText: This formula only returns 'On Sale' when the Event Instance is Active, not AddOnOnly, and the Sale Start Date and Sale End Date are within range
